
Create a Menu driven application to Book a ticket for a Match .
following are the use cases to implements.

Only admin user can access the application so all use are applicable to the admin only

1) 
Maximum 100 tickets can be sold online , 
if admin try to sell more than 100 tickets , it should raise an Exception , OutOfTicketException.

2) 
admin has to Enter the Audiance entry .
one booking can have maximum 6 audiance entry. if not exception should be raised
while adding the Booking , record of Ticket should be saved in List and appropriate Ticket information should be generated in pdf format having following information

-------------------------------------
Ticket Number : 123
Date of Booking : 16 June 2022
Number of Seats : 3
Booking Details 
Seat Number 12  , Name : Mike
Seat Number 13  , Name : Jenny
Seat Number 14  , Name : Alisa
------------------------------------

3)
admin can view all records or records by BookingId

